íŸ@9504df6e71ebc1f50816bfee69acdb4c2b9a4d3f4503fec4dc0385cddd968f0e⁄÷Title: title: Nushell 0.31
Path: Nushell
Content:
natemara fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3407] a slowness in the 
``ps``
 command
elferherrera, kubouch, stormasm, LhKipp ported commands to the new engine-p style
fdncred improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3370] binaryview
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3375] added check for endian-ness, added a bytes and skip
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3374] added ability to change "#" color using header_color
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3367] tweaked the error handling to show specific errors
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3366] updated to a quicker Levenshtein implementation
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3351] allowed start to handle urls
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3359] fixed table-pager feature compilation
Azgrom created a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3388] features cargo installer wrapper
jgoday added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3387] ignore-case and duplicated options to 
``uniq``
 command 
, and fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3354] reduce --numbered bug
ammkrn fixed a panic in the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3382] rustyline helper
Sciencentistguy fixed an 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3358] array index out of bounds error in nu_protocol::value::levenshtein_distance()
ccde177b5fb9b8c55078417b4c9fee removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3349] ichwh
LhKipp fixed an issue 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3344] in nu-env if 
``cd``
 with shortcuts
